  }, "v3"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y v\xE2ng l\u1EDDi CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF con. H\xE3y v\xE2ng theo c\xE1c \u0111i\u1EC1u \u0111\xF2i h\u1ECFi, m\u1EC7nh l\u1EC7nh, lu\u1EADt l\u1EC7, v\xE0 qui t\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a Ng\xE0i \u0111\xE3 ghi trong c\xE1c l\u1EDDi gi\xE1o hu\u1EA5n c\u1EE7a M\xF4-se. N\u1EBFu con l\xE0m nh\u1EEFng nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF th\xEC b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 vi\u1EC7c g\xEC con l\xE0m hay con \u0111i \u0111\xE2u th\xEC con c\u0169ng s\u1EBD th\xE0nh c\xF4ng. "), mdx("h6", {
