  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "V\xE0 n\u1EBFu con v\xE2ng l\u1EDDi CH\xDAA, Ng\xE0i s\u1EBD gi\u1EEF l\u1EDDi h\u1EE9a Ng\xE0i l\u1EADp c\xF9ng ta. Ng\xE0i h\u1EE9a: N\u1EBFu d\xF2ng d\xF5i ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1ED1ng theo nh\u01B0 ta d\u1EB7n v\xE0 ho\xE0n to\xE0n tin c\u1EADy ta, th\xEC trong gia \u0111\xECnh ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xFAc n\xE0o c\u0169ng c\xF3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xE0m vua tr\xEAn \xCDt-ra-en. "), mdx("h6", {
