  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "Ngo\xE0i ra, con \u0111\u1EEBng qu\xEAn \u0111i\u1EC1u Gi\xF4-\xE1p, con X\xEA-ru-gia l\xE0m cho cha. N\xF3 gi\u1EBFt hai v\u1ECB ch\u1EC9 huy c\u1EE7a qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i \xCDt-ra-en: \xC1p-ne, con N\xEA-r\u01A1, v\xE0 A-ma-sa, con Gie-th\xEA. N\xF3 h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng nh\u01B0 th\u1EC3 n\xF3 v\xE0 nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u1EA5y \u0111ang chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u v\u1EDBi nhau nh\u01B0ng th\u1EADt ra l\xE0 \u0111ang h\xF2a b\xECnh. N\xF3 l\xE0 t\xEAn kh\xE1t m\xE1u, v\u1EA5y m\xE1u \u0111\u1EA7y m\xECnh . "), mdx("h6", {
