  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "V\xE0 h\xE3y nh\u1EDB r\u1EB1ng Si-m\xEA-i, con Gh\xEA-ra, ng\u01B0\u1EDDi B\xEAn-gia-min, t\u1EEB Ba-hu-rim \u0111ang \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y v\u1EDBi con. N\xF3 ch\u1EEDi r\u1EE7a ta trong ng\xE0y ta ch\u1EA1y \u0111\u1EBFn Ma-ha-na-im. Nh\u01B0ng khi n\xF3 \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xF3n ta \u1EDF s\xF4ng Gi\xF4-\u0111anh, ta \u0111\xE3 h\u1EE9a v\u1EDBi n\xF3 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t CH\xDAA r\u1EB1ng, 'Si-m\xEA-i, ta s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng gi\u1EBFt ng\u01B0\u01A1i.' "), mdx("h6", {
