  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng con ch\u1EDB n\xEAn \u0111\u1EC3 n\xF3 tho\xE1t kh\u1ECFi tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t. Con l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi kh\xF4n ngoan, bi\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ED1i x\u1EED v\u1EDBi n\xF3 ra sao, nh\u01B0ng con ph\u1EA3i x\u1EED t\u1EED n\xF3.\" "), mdx("h6", {
