  }, "v16"), mdx("p", null, "Nay t\xF4i c\xF3 m\u1ED9t \u0111i\u1EC1u mu\u1ED1n xin b\xE0; xin b\xE0 \u0111\u1EEBng t\u1EEB ch\u1ED1i.\" B\xE1t-s\xEA-ba h\u1ECFi, \"Ng\u01B0\u01A1i mu\u1ED1n \u0111i\u1EC1u g\xEC?\" "), mdx("h6", {
