  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1EADy B\xE1t-s\xEA-ba v\xE0o n\xF3i chuy\u1EC7n v\u1EDBi S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n gi\xF9m cho A-\u0111\xF4-ni-gia. Khi S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n th\u1EA5y b\xE0 li\u1EC1n \u0111\u1EE9ng l\xEAn kh\u1ECFi ngai, c\xFAi ch\xE0o r\u1ED3i ng\u1ED3i xu\u1ED1ng. \xD4ng b\u1EA3o \u0111\u1EA7y t\u1EDB mang m\u1ED9t c\xE1i ngai kh\xE1c cho b\xE0 ng\u1ED3i. R\u1ED3i b\xE0 ng\u1ED3i k\u1EBF b\xEAn ph\u1EA3i vua. "), mdx("h6", {
