  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1EAFn \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EBFt hai ng\u01B0\u1EDDi t\u1ED1t h\u01A1n h\u1EAFn: \xC1p-ne, con N\xEA-r\u01A1, ch\u1EC9 huy qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i \xCDt-ra-en, v\xE0 A-ma-sa, con Gie-th\xEA, ch\u1EC9 huy qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i Giu-\u0111a m\xE0 cha ta kh\xF4ng hay bi\u1EBFt g\xEC. Cho n\xEAn CH\xDAA s\u1EBD b\xE1o tr\u1EA3 n\xF3 v\u1EC1 nh\u1EEFng c\xE1i ch\u1EBFt \u0111\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
