  }, "v45"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng CH\xDAA s\u1EBD ban ph\xFAc cho ta v\xE0 ng\xF4i c\u1EE7a \u0110a-v\xEDt s\u1EBD an to\xE0n \u0111\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EDDi tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t Ng\xE0i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
